
When installing postgres through asdf, add the following
to the postgresql.conf file located in...

.asdf/install/postgres/<version>/data/postgresql.conf


listen_addresses = ''
unix_socket_directories = '/home/darren/.pgdata'

Some documentation for upgrading majors:

https://www.postgresql.org/docs/current/upgrading.html#UPGRADING-VIA-PGDUMPALL

